Accelerated Drinker	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Accelerated Drinker],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait]	DESC:You know how to drink a potion efficiently, such as by not using your hands, tossing it in the air and catching it in your mouth, or opening it with your teeth. You may drink a potion as a move action instead of a standard as long as you start your turn with the potion in your hand.								SOURCEPAGE:p.18
